Kane said: “It was a great experience for me and there is no doubt it was a big stepping stone to where I am now. 
“I was only 18 and it was my first time in the Championship. Harry Kane scores a hat-trick against Fulham in the FA Cup fifth round 
"Everyone knows it can be a tough place to play but I learnt so much in a short space of time and it definitely helped me grow up.” 
The England star scored his second hat-trick of 2017 in Tottenham's 3-0 thrashing of Fulham on Sunday.
